<div class="usage-guide">
  <h2>アプリの使い方</h2>
  <div class="flex items-center justify-center">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-2">
    <!-- 左側：ステップ1 -->
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-start space-y-2 mb-10">
        <button class="self-start inline-flex px-6 py-3 font-medium text-white bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-500 to-orange-600 rounded-full hover:from-orange-600 hover:to-orange-700 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md lg:px-6 lg:py-3 lg:w-auto transition-all duration-200 mb-6">ステップ1</button>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-xl">ログイン</h3>
          <p>メールアドレスとパスワードを入力してログインしてください</p>
          <%= image_tag "screenshots/dashboard.png", class: "screenshot w-100 h-auto" %>
      </div>
  
    <!-- 右側：ログイン後画面 -->
      <div class="flex flex-col items-center justify-start space-y-10 mt-20 mb-26 ">
        <p>ログイン後画面</p>
        <%= image_tag "screenshots/dashboard1.jpg", class: "screenshot w-100 h-auto" %>
        <%= image_tag "screenshots/dashboard2.png", class: "screenshot w-140 h-auto" %>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

    <div class="flex justify-center space-x-34 mb-24">
      <button class="btn-organizer inline-flex px-6 py-3 font-medium text-white bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-500 to-orange-600 rounded-full hover:from-orange-600 hover:to-orange-700 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md lg:px-14 lg:py-5 lg:w-auto transition-all duration-200">開催者の方</button>
      <button class="btn-exhibitor inline-flex px-6 py-3 font-medium text-white bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-500 to-orange-600 rounded-full hover:from-orange-600 hover:to-orange-700 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md lg:px-14 lg:py-5 lg:w-auto transition-all duration-200">出展者の方</button>
      <button class="btn-participant inline-flex px-6 py-3 font-medium text-white bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-500 to-orange-600 rounded-full hover:from-orange-600 hover:to-orange-700 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md lg:px-14 lg:py-5 lg:w-auto transition-all duration-200">参加者の方</button>
    </div>

    <div id="organizer-section">
      <h2 class="font-bold text-xl">開催者向け使い方</h2>
    <!-- 開催者向けの説明内容 -->
    </div>
  <div class="grid grid-cols-4 gap-4">
    <div class="step">
      <div class="flex items-center justify-start space-x-4 mb-4 mt-4">
        <button class="inline-flex px-6 py-3 font-medium text-white bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-500 to-orange-600 rounded-full hover:from-orange-600 hover:to-orange-700 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md lg:px-6 lg:py-3 lg:w-auto transition-all duration-200">
        ステップ1
        </button>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-xl">マルシェ作成</h3>
      </div>  
      <p>各項目を入力して自分のマルシェの魅力を伝えましょう</p>
      <%= image_tag "screenshots/dashboard3.png", class: "screenshot w-60 h-auto" %>
    </div>

     <div class="step mt-24">
      <p>作成したマルシェ</p>
      <%= image_tag "screenshots/dashboard5.png", class: "screenshot w-150 h-auto " %>
    </div>

    <div class="step">
      <div class="flex items-center justify-start space-x-4 mb-4 mt-4">
        <button class="inline-flex px-6 py-3 font-medium text-white bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-500 to-orange-600 rounded-full hover:from-orange-600 hover:to-orange-700 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md lg:px-6 lg:py-3 lg:w-auto transition-all duration-200">
        ステップ2
        </button>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-xl">Myページ/Myマルシェを確認</h3>
    </div>  
      <p>作成したマルシェが表示されています</p>
      <p>出店申請がある場合</p>
      <%= image_tag "screenshots/dashboard7.png", class: "screenshot w-96 h-auto" %>
    </div>

    <div class="step mt-16">
      <p>出展者情報が表示されます</p>
      <p>ステータスは「選定中」で登録されます</p>
      <%= image_tag "screenshots/dashboard9.png", class: "screenshot w-90 h-auto " %>
    </div>

    <div class="step">
      <div class="flex items-center justify-start space-x-4 mb-4 mt-4">
        <button class="inline-flex px-6 py-3 font-medium text-white bg-gradient-to-r from-orange-500 to-orange-600 rounded-full hover:from-orange-600 hover:to-orange-700 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md lg:px-6 lg:py-3 lg:w-auto transition-all duration-200">
        ステップ3
        </button>
        <h3 class="font-bold text-xl">出展者確定</h3>
      </div>  
      <p>自身のマルシェに出店してもらう出展者を決めよう</p>
      <p>「確定」と更新すると「共有」の痰が表示されます</p>
      <%= image_tag "screenshots/dashboard10.png", class: "screenshot w-90 h-auto" %>
    </div>

    <div class="step mt-16">
      <p>確定した出展者に情報を共有できます</p>
      <p>このページは開催者のみ編集可能です</p>
      <%= image_tag "screenshots/dashboard9.png", class: "screenshot w-90 h-auto " %>
    </div>
  


   <div id="exhibitor-section">
      <h2>出展者向け使い方</h2>
  <!-- 出展者向けの説明内容 -->
    </div>

    <div id="participant-section">
      <h2>参加者向け使い方</h2>
    <!-- 参加者向けの説明内容 -->
    </div>
    
  
</div>